cs.assignments.graphs

Class MinPriorityQ<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs.assignments.graphs.MinPriorityQ<K>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - Priority type.

    public class MinPriorityQ<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Minimum priority queue implemented with a minimum binary heap. This implementation is borrowed, in part, from the books implementation of IndexMinPQ#java. After trying doing my own the book's proved to be more elegant and faster. I altered my code to match the book's where necessary.
    Author:
    Robert Wilk
